powers: Tae was a god and had superhuman strength greater than that of the demi-god Hercules, as well as a high resistance to injury. Tae was able to perform such feats as controlling the weather, firing energy blasts from his hands, and together with Pennsu could create a devastating beam capable of destroying a planet. Together, Tae and Pennsu boasted that they also had the ability to create new worlds and new denizens to worship them.
